ORBS staking guide (version 20200429.0.1)
You selected “LEDGER” and “Android”
How to stake ORBS with “ORBS PoS Wallet”
Please follow the instruction
1. Install “ORBS PoS Wallet” on your android device (click here to install)
2. Run installed app and connect LEDGER (USB or BT) to the app

ORBS staking guide (version 20200429.0.1)
You selected “Samsung Blockchain”
(This is only available in some new Samsung Galaxy devices)
How to stake ORBS with “ORBS PoS Wallet”
Please follow the instruction
1. Install “ORBS PoS Wallet” on your Samsung device (click here to install)
2. Run installed app and connect Samsung Keystore when you select mode
ORBS staking guide (version 20200429.0.1)
You selected “Status” and “Android”
Please follow the instruction
1. Install “Status wallet” on your android device (click here to install)
2. Please connect TETRA (staking.orbs.network) in embedded dapp browser.
3. Make sure you have tokens and gas fee in you account.
4. Follow TETRA tutorial.
